title: GETTIN’ RAUNCHY WITH CHRISTIAN
description: Ready to get raunchy? Christian Franceschi is this week’s co-host and is nothing short of amazing. You want to learn the ins and and outs of partying in NYC? Tune in to get an earful of booze, booty calls, and babes. Oh, and don’t forget the ASMR!
